<item>
            <title>[CAMEL-4324] Response body lost when an HTTP error code is returned</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CAMEL-4324</link>
                <project id="12311211" key="CAMEL">Camel</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When a REST service returns an HTTP error code (e.g. 404) with some content in the response body, this body is not correctly copied into the exception.&lt;br/&gt;
This results e.g. in ${exception.responseBody} having a value like &quot;org.restlet.data.Response@17bf0a7&quot; in the following route fragment :&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;lt;doTry&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
    &amp;lt;to uri=&quot;restlet:&lt;a href=&quot;http://my.service.com/ws/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://my.service.com/ws/&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
{id}
&lt;p&gt;&quot;/&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
    &amp;lt;doCatch&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
        &amp;lt;exception&amp;gt;org.apache.camel.CamelException&amp;lt;/exception&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
        &amp;lt;log message=&quot;body is : ${exception.responseBody}&quot;/&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
    &amp;lt;/doCatch&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&amp;lt;/doTry&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The problem is probably due to the statement (class org.apache.camel.component.restlet.RestletProducer, method populateRestletProducerException) :&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;   &lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;String&lt;/span&gt; copy = response.toString();
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;that should be instead something like :&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;   &lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;String&lt;/span&gt; copy = &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;null&lt;/span&gt;;
   &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; (response.getEntity() != &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;null&lt;/span&gt;) {
       &lt;span class=&quot;code-comment&quot;&gt;// get content text
&lt;/span&gt;       copy = response.getEntity().getText();
   }
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
</description>
